data.description: Welcome to this incredible townhome located in the highly desirable area of Alpharetta, Georgia. Minutes away from Downtown Alpharetta, Avalon, Windward shopping and easy access to highway 400. The main living area offers a comfortable flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, with a view to the extended patio. This home offers freshly painted rooms with beautiful hardwood flooring throughout. The kitchen has beautiful granite counter tops with stainless Steel appliances. The main level also has a fireplace, half bath and a spacious laundry room. The primary bedroom offers a large walk in closet with an ensuite with double vanity, tub and shower. The upstairs also has two secondary bedrooms. The well-maintained community offers a swimming pool and playground. Don't miss on a chance to make this your home.
